title: Clive Brittain saddles final runner at Newbury
text: Clive Brittain saddles final runner at Newbury Saturday, 24 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) CLIVE BRITTAIN will bid a quiet farewell to the sport and profession of which he has been one of the outstanding pioneers when he sends out his final runner at Newbury today.
